description: Math Dog is your personal math tutor, giving you math problems to solve with increasing difficulty as you master each level.  Questions start with basic addition, and progress up to include subtraction, multiplication and division.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Math Dog to begin.
Alexa, ask Math Dog to change difficulty.
name: Math Dog
shortDescription: A quiz style math game to help users master basic math facts.  Fun for kindergarten to adults.
